# Conda-forge Installation Workflow

**Policy authority:** See `AGENTS.md` → "Tooling and dependencies".

This rule applies **only** when dependency, environment, or tooling configuration is being added or modified.

## Procedure

Always run a dry-run check before installing via conda-forge:

```bash
# Check availability and conflicts first
mamba install -c conda-forge --dry-run <package(s)>

# Only if dry-run succeeds, install
mamba install -c conda-forge <package(s)>